Frontend: Single-page web app (SPA) built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for rapid prototyping.

Backend: Node.js with Express for serving RESTful APIs and static assets.

Database: SQLite (via better-sqlite3) for fast, file-based persistence of scenarios.

API Layer: REST endpoints handle simulation, CRUD for saved scenarios, and gated report generation.

Deployment: Runs locally (Node.js) or deployable via Render/Vercel with minor modifications.
